Write an SQL query that makes recommendations using the pages that your
 friends liked.
 Assume you have two tables: a two-column table of users and their friends,
 and a two-column table of users and the pages they liked.
 It should not recommend pages you already like.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
2- Statistics: -Research Design Question: How would you test whether having
 more friends now 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
order and unique in R
