\begin_layout Standard
The ultimate goal for any modeling team is to develop robust and flexible
 models that can last long.
 One the model was developed, the rest of part is just daily routine, is
 just to maintain the model and use the model
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
How many 
\series bold
percentage of time is for daily-routine
\series default
 work, and
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
When one team starts to develop models and build new procedures or prototype,
 everything is so really exciting.
 But when you finished developing those things, everything will become so
 mature and developed, and what left is just maintenance.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
