 like the result of your model, for example, your forecasting may suggest
 a completely opposite story that the management committee believe.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In my case, I'm doing loss forecasting for marketing.
 They question my model only when the loss forecasting is too high and kill
 their campaign.
